"more information."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1696
msgid ""
"`#5764 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5764>`_: New behavior of "
"the ``--pastebin`` option: failures to connect to the pastebin server are "
"reported, without failing the pytest run"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1703 ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:2244
msgid ""
"`#5806 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5806>`_: Fix \"lexer\" "
"being used when uploading to bpaste.net from ``--pastebin`` to \"text\"."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1706
msgid ""
"`#5884 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5884>`_: Fix ``--setup-"
"only`` and ``--setup-show`` for custom pytest items."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1713
msgid ""
"`#5056 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5056>`_: The "
"HelpFormatter uses ``py.io.get_terminal_width`` for better width detection."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1717
msgid "pytest 5.1.3 (2019-09-18)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1722
msgid ""
"`#5807 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5807>`_: Fix pypy3.6 "
"(nightly) on windows."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1725
msgid ""
"`#5811 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5811>`_: Handle ``--"
"fulltrace`` correctly with ``pytest.raises``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1728
msgid ""
"`#5819 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5819>`_: Windows: Fix "
"regression with conftest whose qualified name contains uppercase characters "
"(introduced by #5792)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1733
msgid "pytest 5.1.2 (2019-08-30)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1738
msgid ""
"`#2270 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/2270>`_: Fixed ``self`` "
"reference in function-scoped fixtures defined plugin classes: previously "
"``self`` would be a reference to a *test* class, not the *plugin* class."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1742
msgid ""
"`#570 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/570>`_: Fixed long "
"standing issue where fixture scope was not respected when indirect fixtures "
"were used during parametrization."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1746
msgid ""
"`#5782 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5782>`_: Fix decoding "
"error when printing an error response from ``--pastebin``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1749
msgid ""
"`#5786 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5786>`_: Chained "
"exceptions in test and collection reports are now correctly serialized, "
"allowing plugins like ``pytest-xdist`` to display them properly."
