msgid ""
"`#4344 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/4344>`_: Fix "
"RuntimeError/StopIteration when trying to collect package with \"__init__."
"py\" only."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1858
msgid ""
"`#5115 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5115>`_: Warnings issued "
"during ``pytest_configure`` are explicitly not treated as errors, even if "
"configured as such, because it otherwise completely breaks pytest."
