#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1861 ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:2223
msgid ""
"`#5477 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5477>`_: The XML file "
"produced by ``--junitxml`` now correctly contain a ``<testsuites>`` root "
