#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1881
msgid ""
"`#5634 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5634>`_: ``pytest.exit`` "
"is now correctly handled in ``unittest`` cases. This makes ``unittest`` "
"cases handle ``quit`` from pytest's pdb correctly."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1885 ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:2276
msgid ""
"`#5650 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5650>`_: Improved output "
"when parsing an ini configuration file fails."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1888
msgid ""
"`#5701 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5701>`_: Fix collection "
"of ``staticmethod`` objects defined with ``functools.partial``."
