"but this could be incorrect due to delayed parsing of options for plugins. "
"See for example issues `#1149 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/"
"issues/1149>`__, `#3413 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/"
"issues/3413>`__, and `#4009 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/"
"issues/4009>`__."
