#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:2029
msgid ""
"`#3457 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/3457>`_: New "
"`pytest_assertion_pass <https://docs.pytest.org/en/stable/reference."
"html#_pytest.hookspec.pytest_assertion_pass>`__ hook, called with context "
"information when an assertion *passes*."
msgstr ""

