#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:2035
msgid ""
"`#5440 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5440>`_: The "
"`faulthandler <https://docs.python.org/3/library/faulthandler.html>`__ "
"standard library module is now enabled by default to help users diagnose "
"crashes in C modules."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:2038
msgid ""
"This functionality was provided by integrating the external `pytest-"
"faulthandler <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest-faulthandler>`__ plugin "
"into the core, so users should remove that plugin from their requirements if "
"used."
