#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:2045
msgid ""
"`#5452 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5452>`_: When warnings "
"are configured as errors, pytest warnings now appear as originating from "
"``pytest.`` instead of the internal ``_pytest.warning_types.`` module."
