"makes the exit code available for consumer code and are more explicit other "
"than just documentation. User defined exit codes are still valid, but should "
"be used with caution."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:2050
msgid ""
"The team doesn't expect this change to break test suites or plugins in "
"general, except in esoteric/specific scenarios."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:2052
