"`#5239 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/5239>`_: Pin ``pluggy`` "
"to ``< 1.0`` so we don't update to ``1.0`` automatically when it gets "
"released: there are planned breaking changes, and we want to ensure pytest "
"properly supports ``pluggy 1.0``."
