#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:6496
msgid ""
"Removed code and documentation for Python 2.5 or lower versions, including "
"removal of the obsolete ``_pytest.assertion.oldinterpret`` module. Thanks "
"`@nicoddemus`_ for the PR (`#1226`_)."
